# NetworkCompatibilityToken.Compatibility.compatible

**Case**

An indication that the compared devices are running compatible versions of RealityKit.

## Declaration

```swift
case compatible
```

## Compatibility indicators

- **NetworkCompatibilityToken.Compatibility.sessionProtocolVersionMismatch**: An indication that two peers running incompatible versions of RealityKit can’t sync.
